metadata.description: In ancient China, people described Chang'er as a legendary figure who lives on the moon, with a rabbit as her loyal companion.  Fast forward to now, when the price of Bitcoin is soaring TO THE MOON! This captured Chang'er’s attention, who flew down to earth to see what all the fuss is about. While resting on the famous ferris wheel overseeing Hong Kong Victoria Harbour, Chang-er decided she’s going to chill here for a while, after all what’s the rush?
metadata.name: Chang’e 2021 by Benny SY Li
